   Three Police Chiefs Serve as Community Champions for �March For Wheels�
</div><br><br />
<br />
    Across the nation during the week of March 17, local officials took part in Meals On Wheels �Community Champions Week� to raise awareness for senior hunger.  Three local police chiefs from Summit, Springfield and New Providence gathered together at SAGE Eldercare on Wednesday, March 19 to participate in this event and deliver meals to residents in their respective towns.  
